<ab>+ <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Pikembach und
                                                  <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                                Miltemberg<lb/>+ Diethern Lantschaden, vicztum zu
                                                  Aschaffemburg<lb/><expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
